# Next Steps

#### Thank you for completing **Music Lab** Now that you've learned some basic computer science skills, check out some of our curriculum and professional learning offerings to continue your journey!

## Teach CS in your class

#### Explore some of these curriculum options to get started teaching CS in your class right away.


<div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 20px; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 1200px;">
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); grid-gap: 20px; width: 100%;">
    <!-- Top Row -->
    <div style="text-align: center; background-color: #F7F8FA; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
