      </a>
      <p style="font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"><a href="https://code.org/educate/csc" target="_blank">Computer Science Connections</a>
      <ul style="text-align: left; font-size: 14pt;"> 
       Make connections between CS and other subjects like math, language arts, science, and social studies. 
       
 
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center; background-color: #F7F8FA; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
      <img src="https://images.code.org/daf3e86ac354a50461ac80727eeada1a-image-1739218585084.24.20 AM.png" alt="thumbnail for the CS Fundamentals curriculum " width="240px" style="width: 150px; height: 150px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 10px;">
      <p style="font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"> <a href = "https://code.org/educate/csf" target="_blank">Computer Science Fundamentals</a>
   
      <ul style="text-align: left; font-size: 14pt;">
   Free, and fun, elementary courses for each grade to introduce your students to CS. 
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    
    <div style="text-align: center; background-color: #F7F8FA; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
      <img src="https://images.code.org/2693b34cb023a483fbe3cd484155a71b-image-1739218636352.24.25 AM.png" alt="thumbnail for the CS Connections self-paced professional learniing module " style="width: 150px; height: 150px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 10px;">
      <p style="font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"><a href = "https://studio.code.org/s/oceans" target="_blank">AI for Oceans</a>
      <ul style="text-align: left; font-size: 14pt;">
 In this fun introduction to artificial intelligence, you train a real machine learning model to identify sea creatures and trash in the ocean. 
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
