## Continue learning 
#### Learn more about teaching CS with these self-paced professional learning modules. 

<div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 20px; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 1200px;">
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); grid-gap: 20px; width: 100%;">
    <!-- Top Row -->
    <div style="text-align: center; background-color: #F7F8FA; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
     <img src="https://images.code.org/e8301a302ae70bd183b768394bab2b60-image-1739218699282.24.56 AM.png" alt="thumbnail for the CS Connections self-paced professional learniing module " style="width: 150px; height: 100px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 10px;">
      <p style="font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"> <a href = "https://studio.code.org/s/self-paced-pl-csc-2023" target="blank" >Teaching Computer Science Connections</a>
      <ul style="text-align: left; font-size: 14pt;">
        This course prepares you to teach the CS Connections Modules to learn creative ways to implement CS into core content areas. 
       
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center; background-color: #F7F8FA; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
     <img src="https://images.code.org/e9ad803b6c30599a545869bc2a38efe8-image-1739218971069.24.49 AM.png" alt="thumbnail for the CS Fundamentals self-paced professional learniing module " style="width: 150px; height: 100px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 10px;">
      <p style="font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"> <a href = "https://studio.code.org/s/k5-onlinepd-2023"target="blank" >Teaching Computer Science Fundamentals</a> </p>
      <ul style="text-align: left; font-size: 14pt;">
     This course prepares you to teach the CS Fundamentals courses and learn effective ways to teach CS to grades K-5. 
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    
    <div style="text-align: center; background-color: #F7F8FA; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
      <img src="https://images.code.org/d29a62cb389de6dc363f6fda28057df1-image-1739219020041.24.45 AM.png" alt="thumbnail for the CS Basicss self-paced professional learniing module "  style="width: 150px; height: 100px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 10px;">
      <p style="font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"><a href = "https://studio.code.org/s/self-paced-pl-k5-2024-2"target="blank" >Computer Science Basics for K-5 Teachers</a>  </p>
      <ul style="text-align: left; font-size: 14pt;">
The interactive module teaches basic vocabulary and concepts to help you get started bringing out student creativity in CS with Sprite Lab. 
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
  


